text: Goephanes pacificus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaire in 1897.Biolib.cz - Goephanes. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Goephanes Category:Beetles described in 1897 Category:Taxa named by Léon Fairmaire
